General.Name: Wingara AG Ltd
General.Description: Wingara AG Limited engages in processing and marketing agricultural products in Australia. It offers oaten hay and other fodder products. The company also exports its products to Asia. In addition, it provides temperature-controlled facilities, blast freezing, and storage and distribution services. The company was formerly known as Biron Apparel Limited and changed its name to Wingara AG Limited in January 2016. Wingara AG Limited was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Hawthorn, Australia.
